OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FA robber who ambushed an elderly man
OL,7,Fand snatched a #30,000 watch from his
OL,8,Fwrist on a central London street has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FZakaria Senouci has been sentenced to
OL,12,Fthree years and nine months in prison.
OL,14,FZakaria Senouci was "handsomely
OL,15,Frewarded" for the "unpleasant street
OL,16,Frobbery" in April 2025 which left the
OL,17,F73 year old victim so anxious that he
OL,18,Fnow plans to move abroad, Southwark
OL,19,FCrown Court heard.
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@IO]wD@SOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
