OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FCCTV showed Senouci "loitering" with
OL,7,Fanother hooded accomplice on the
OL,8,Fcorner of a street near Hyde Park
OL,9,Fbefore sprinting towards Sunil Chopra,
OL,10,Fgrabbing his left arm and ripping the
OL,11,FPatek Philippe watch from his wrist.
OL,13,FMr Chopra could be seen in the footage
OL,14,Fto have spun around after his arm was
OL,15,Fpulled, and he then saw Senouci
OL,16,Ffleeing down the street with the watch.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FSenouci, an Algerian national who
OL,7,Fchanged his plea to guilty to robbery
OL,8,Fon the first day of his trial last
OL,9,Fmonth, was on Thursday sentenced to
OL,10,Fthree years and nine months in prison.
OL,12,FAs an asylum seeker, his case will be
OL,13,Freferred to the Secretary of State for
OL,14,Fa decision on deportation at the end
OL,15,Fof his sentence, the court heard.
OL,17,FThe watch, which Mr Chopra had hoped
OL,18,Fto pass on to his son, was not insured
OL,19,Fand has not been seen again.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Mark Weekes told
OL,7,FSenouci:
OL,9,F"CCTV and cell site evidence show that
OL,10,Fyou and another individual had
OL,11,Ftravelled to the area and were
OL,12,Floitering for some time, the obvious
OL,13,Finference is that you were seeking a
OL,14,Fsuitable target for your activities
OL,15,Fthat night.
OL,17,F"You see Mr Chopra approach. You
OL,18,Fallowed him to pass. You yanked from
OL,19,Fhim a very valuable watch.
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,F"It was taken with sufficient violence
OL,7,Fto cause a scratch to the arm and a
OL,8,Ftear to his shirt sleeve."
OL,10,FThe judge said of the watch:
OL,12,F"It was of profound sentimental
OL,13,Fimportance to Mr Chopra, and his
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,F"The intention was that it was to be
OL,17,Fpassed on to his son as a family
OL,18,Fheirloom."
OL,26,@pD@ZO]tD@AOUxD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FThe judge described it as "an
OL,7,Funpleasant street robbery" on an
OL,8,Felderly victim as he walked home in
OL,9,Fbroad daylight. He said:
OL,11,F"He was entitled to feel safe in his
OL,12,Fown neighbourhood ` he no longer does."
OL,14,FA year after the robbery, the victim
OL,15,Fis "hyper vigilant" and is making
OL,16,Fplans to leave the country, the court
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@ZO]sD@AOUtD@gO]wD@DOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FMr Chopra no longer feels safe, has
OL,7,Fanxiety, the robbery has altered his
OL,8,Fbehaviour so he tries to avoid risk,
OL,9,Fand he has nightmares.
OL,11,FThe judge added: "Tragically as a
OL,12,Fconsequence of the offence, he no
OL,13,Flonger feels safe in this wonderful
OL,14,Fcountry and thinks he may have to
OL,15,Fleave the UK."
OL,17,FSenouci had willingly taken part in
OL,18,Fthe theft although others may have
OL,19,Fbeen involved in the planning of it,
OL,20,Fthe court heard.
OL,26,@sD@ROUwD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
