OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FSenouci claimed he was encouraged to
OL,7,Fsteal by a person he had met and was
OL,8,Fpromised E1,000 for the robbery but
OL,9,Fwas paid E700 .
OL,11,FThe judge told him "you were
OL,12,Fhandsomely rewarded" even though the
OL,13,Famount was not as expected, "for an
OL,14,Fhours' work preying on an elderly man."
OL,16,FSenouci's "involvement was voluntary"
OL,17,Fin an "opportunistic plan" to steal,
OL,18,Fthe judge said.
OL,26,@pD@JOkqD@JOksD@TOUtD@TO]uD@]OUxD@KOUxD@
OL,26,AeO]yD@GOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
