OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FEarlier Senouci's defence counsel
OL,7,FElega Simpson said he recalled feeling
OL,8,F"scared at the time" of the robbery,
OL,9,Fadding that it was the high value
OL,10,Fwatch and not Mr Chopra specifically
OL,11,Fwhich had been targeted.
OL,13,FShe said: "Regrettably the watch was
OL,14,Fhanded to another individual. He has
OL,15,Fno idea what happened to it."
OL,17,FSimpson continued: "He regrets his
OL,18,Factions. He did not intend to cause
OL,19,Fharm to Mr Chopra."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]uD@KOUwD@]O]yD@TOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
