PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777050358
OL,3,CRobber who ripped #30,000 watch from
OL,4,Cwrist of pensioner jailed
OL,6,FSenouci is a mechanic and applied for
OL,7,Fasylum after arriving in the UK at the
OL,8,Fage of 22.
OL,10,FHe hopes to turn his life around and
OL,11,Fhelp his family when he is released,
OL,12,Fthe court heard.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
